These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
Hobby: board-games, hiking
Job: doctor, dancer
1. Job:doctor is in an even position##4
2. Job:dancer == Hobby:hiking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | hiking | board-games |
| Job     | dancer    | doctor   |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
Beverage: milk, water
Sport: skateboarding, skiing
1. Sport:skateboarding is in an odd position##4
2. Beverage:water is on the left of Beverage:milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Beverage   | water | milk        |
| Sport      | skateboarding  | skiing |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
Music-Genre: gospel, punk
Nationality: chinese, spanish
1. Nationality:chinese is in an odd position##4
2. Music-Genre:punk is on the left of Music-Genre:gospel##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | punk    | gospel |
| Nationality   | chinese | spanish |

